name: JBL TUNE 600BTNC - Headphones with mic - on-ear - Bluetooth - wireless - active noise canceling - black | Dell USA
description: Introducing the JBL TUNE 600BTNC wireless on-ear headphones, a flat-folding lightweight and compact solution for everyday use. JBL sound can be enjoyed without unnecessary noise for hours wirelessly. And thanks to the additional detachable cable, music can be enjoyed endlessly in wired mode. The JBL TUNE 600BTNC allow you to connect to your world quickly thanks to buttons on the ear cups that allow for easy hands-free management of calls and music.
